## [Databases & Local Dev]
# Avoid committing local SQLite database files (if you use SQLite locally)
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

# Avoid committing local secrets and sensitive settings
# (Keep appsettings.json, but IGNORE appsettings.Development.json if it contains local secrets)
# appsettings.Development.json # Uncomment this if you put real database passwords/keys here

# Secrets Manager (where dotnet user-secrets saves keys locally)
secrets.json

